name: Freya
coverLetter:
21 yr old female looking for trim work. Don't have any experience yet but am a hard worker and very reliable. I've worked on (normal) farms, in factories, in below 0 weather for long hours, can work as long as needed. 
I have a van, which is also my house, so I can work anywhere, any state no housing needed. I want to make money, and would love to someday have my own farm.
